   &UR; NATIONAL GENERAL &LR;  (``a'' code)
</P>
<P>
   KIDS-MURDER (Chicago) _ Chicago is reeling as two boys, seven
and eight years old, are charged with first degree murder in the
killing of an 11-year-old apparently killed for her bicycle. By Pam
Belluck.
</P>
