   &UR; (Joel D. Barkan is professor of political science at the
University of Iowa and a senior fellow at the U.S. Institute of
Peace. David F. Gordon is a senior fellow at the Overseas
Development Council. This article is adapted from a longer version
in Foreign Affairs.) &LR;
</P>
<P>
   -------------------- &QC;
</P>
</TEXT>
