<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 1998-08-11 14:57 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A8207 &Cx1f; ttj-z
r f &Cx13;  &Cx11;  BC-SF-ACQUISITIONS-HNS &LR;      08-11 0620
