<SLUG> BC-MEXICO-LABOR-0812-COX </SLUG>
<HEADLINE>
&HT;   
</HEADLINE>
 &HT;    U.S. CRITICIZES MEXICO FOR HEALTH AND SAFETY VIOLATIONS AT
TIJUANA FACTORY
 &HT;    Moving in both the (i) International and (f) Financial
categories.
