PARADISE-MOVIE (Los Angeles) _ Vince Vaughn, Anne Heche and Joaquin
Phoenix enjoyed working with one another so much in the moral
thriller ``Return to Paradise'' that they're already making other
movies together: Vaughn and Phoenix have the black comedy ``Clay
Pigeons'' coming out in October and Vaughn and Heche headline thr
remake of ``Psycho.'' By Bob Strauss. 
