shootings, in which a teacher and four students were killed. After
a two-hour trial, Circuit Judge Ralph Wilson on Tuesday convicted
12-year-old Andrew Golden and found him, along with Mitchell, to be
``delinquent'' - the juvenile court equivalent of a guilty verdict.
(Alan S. Weiner/New York Times Photo)
