Naipaul and Theroux, as mentor and protege, was mutually rewarding
over a period of more than 30 years. Now, with the forthcoming
publication of Theroux's book ``Sir Vidia's Shadow: A Friendship
Across Five Continents,'' and the controversy surrounding it, there
